data.description: Check Out This Beautifully Updated 3 Bedroom/2 Bath Brick Cape Cod! This Home is Situated on a Large Completely Fenced in Lot & It is Not Going to Last in This Market, at This Price! Here We Have the Perfect Backyard for Summer Get-Togethers.  Inside We Have Beautiful Hardwood Flooring & Newer Carpeting in the Bedrooms. The Updated Kitchen Has Newer White Cabinets, Granite Countertops & Newer SS Appliances! The Full Basement is Ready for Your Ideas, Roughed -in Bathroom & Has Exterior Access. Basement Also Has a Finished Room. The Home Has a Newer 30 Agricultual Roof.
